head.note:
In English and Spanish;
                                Spanish text not printed. Ratification advised by the Senate, May
                                31, 1934; ratified by the President, June 5, 1934; ratified by Cuba,
                                June 4, 1934; ratifications exchanged at Washington, June 9, 1934;
                                pro-claimed by the President of the United States, June 9,
                                1934.

div.p:
The Provisional President of the Republic of Cuba, Señor Dr. Manuel
                            Márquez Sterling, Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of the
                            Republic of Cuba to the United States of America;
